We recommended Management to strictly adhere to Section 12 of RA No. 7279, and Sections 4 and 5 of PD No. 957 by implementing the following:

To demand the contracted surveyor to perform its obligation and to submit the latest accomplishment report including the justification as to the reason of delayed delivery of services; 
To facilitate the submission of the Subdivision Plan to DENR Land Management Bureau, the registration of the project and license to sell;
Upon receipt of the registration certificate and license to sell, to execute the Deed of Sale/Contract of Lease to qualified beneficiaries; and
To furnish the Accounting Office with the Deed of Sale/Contract of Lease as documentary requirement for the disposition of residential lots to qualified beneficiaries recorded under Trust Liability-Lugait Resettlement Project.

