We recommended to direct the Municipal Accountant the following measures to attain fairness of presentation of the Cash and Cash Equivalent, in conformity with Paragraph 76 of IPSAS 1;

To discontinue the inclusion of Undelivered and Staled Checks among its Outstanding Checks in preparing its Bank reconciliation Statements; and 
To draw JEV to restore the cash and liabilities pertaining to the stale and undelivered checks.

